Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:39.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}在傍晚搖曳的風中 近在咫尺的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:52.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}我一直 凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:58.86,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.51,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur3\fad(100,100)}一直喜歡著你
