Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子去參加學園祭的慶祝會了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子也開始常常往外跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸 等爽子有了男朋友就不止是往外跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 爽子嫁人的時候就更不止這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不遠了哦 她爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:45.56,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\blur1\3c&HE7BB9A&\c&H834131&}第11話 學園祭之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子他們是不是已經到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家兩個人可是約好了一起去參加慶祝會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等很久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種對話 肯定會出現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真想趕快圍觀她們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會翹掉慶功會 然後兩個人一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我肯定會揍風早的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想偷看一眼的 卻沒偷成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反應算什麼嘛 好受傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷？對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太緊張了 有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 的確是緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有點不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部 我想要你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做夢一樣 爽~子~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 那裡只是牽手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 沒抱上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是牽了個手而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 騙人吧 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想圍觀 太給力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那裡的距離感...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 風早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人沒看到現場版 所以我在給大家重現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學 話說昨天他們還在教室裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以揍你一頓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 剛剛的那算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 風早喜歡貞子嗎 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做夢一樣 是噩夢？還是美夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你倆是一起來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 你們兩個在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額 額 該從哪裡開始說 那個 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 為啥會這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子是怎麼把風早弄到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我喜歡爽子喜歡到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也驚訝啊 我真是同情風早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 這樣回答就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是急死我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 貌似是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是貌似了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}好強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子好強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把風早...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子的名字不是白叫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膜拜下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我也早日成雙成對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情好像朝著神奇的方向發展了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他倆看起來挺幸福的 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了也不會有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:06:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀二年級D班獲得學園祭第六名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以留在他的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於他來說...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可惡 哥的高級壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}討厭啦 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你小子不是三浦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是小痞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子帶著別的班的女生在這裡晃悠什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有自己班的慶功會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去 但是是這邊先邀請我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了痞老師 在這種地方一個人寂寞的喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 老師寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我們班的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜蜜草莓時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白成功版翔太君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊 看起來不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 風早 過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問啦 就一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倆人搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他倆關係有這麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}黑沼 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不要再讓貞子哭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那天貞子在學校後院哭的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為她以為風早喜歡上了別的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有人告訴她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰告訴她的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 不是貞子 是爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以叫她爽子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我還是會用我自己的愛稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你昨天對翔太說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天...我都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓 聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太 給哥過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆 在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 該不會就你一個人這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有清楚直接的對黑沼說過「請和我交往」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 但是她應該明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了 你覺得她是能心領神會的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在趕快去說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她的樣子 好像真的不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾蛋 快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得你能有今天是托了誰的福啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我考慮一下啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}喂 黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用追上去解釋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你都做了些什麼好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這真是最糟糕的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子一看就不是能開玩笑的那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她當真了 你卻告訴她那是個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會很傷心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會傷心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是那啥 別說交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 你小子就等著被甩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就自己去折騰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會早點回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我嫁人了 爸爸會是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還是不說了 忘記我剛剛說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 她爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小痞說的那樣 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結 結婚的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早 你是想說結婚的事情是誤會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想打我的話就打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 再怎麼說我也不會把那種話當真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道 那是荒井老師說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,49)\fs26}請讓我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(191,47)}請讓我妄想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞 哪裡有個洞讓我鑽進去...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼美好的事情 也只能在想像中看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 似乎是我變得太貪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你真的是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的事情 一定要清楚的告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 就會永遠止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠好好珍惜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠 永遠...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有件重要的事情沒有告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了不要討厭我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會討厭你的 有什麼話就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有辦法用不帶私心的眼神去看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會討厭你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 根本用不著擔心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 讓人羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 說實話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 只是覺得他倆太般配了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真是不該說他是離爽子最遠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對誰說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對誰說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對風早...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早和爽子鬧彆扭之前...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放過她吧 結果好就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 去找其他班的女生去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 千草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C班也有二次聚會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子呢 甜蜜草莓時間中？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手嘛 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(這不是夢)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(NOT夢 去看日記吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(看啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\pos(374,72)\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&}注意 特別強調 這篇日記不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&\pos(321,252)}他穿著很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&\pos(545,247)}這是我縫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\frz17.883\c&H62695D&\3c&HD7DBCF&\pos(684,137)}慶功會的時候 他穿的是便裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡醒之後 怎麼想都覺得這是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺之前自己做的這一堆準備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是真的啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似大家都在討論什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用黑魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子把風早？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說告白的時候風早的眼睛是紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡 喜歡 歡喜 歡...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖 那不是完全被操縱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說我就能接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搶 按順序來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡排隊做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受過被魔法咨詢的人可是全部都告白成功了誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人敬畏吧 被人膜拜吧 爽子已經成神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收費吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像騙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 要真有那麼好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子不早就找到一個超好的男人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 周圍淨是些和尚頭 廢柴和笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有遭人騷擾真是萬幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看來沒什麼可擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式神有不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 風早...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也相信我有魔力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 現在還在想這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐都懶得吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我一直都喜歡她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候眼睛真的紅了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早說了 他只是一直都喜歡爽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說了 就像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們知道什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的班的人也都聚在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就把話說清楚 讓他們都閉嘴不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們爽子是你的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好生動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接用了一個現實感十足的詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在真的滿心都是傾心已久得償所願的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就不要煩我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 整理一下就是這樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(160,7)}就像做夢一樣（上）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\pos(676,9)}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(606,231)}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}傾心已久\N想要你的全部\N甜蜜草莓時間(中)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(462,340)}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}男朋友     重度癡迷      女朋友（下）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(242,213)\frz20.53}{\3c&H687A73&\c&HFFFFFF&}非\N常\N非\N常\N喜\N歡\N（左）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就請大家幫忙廣為宣傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說不要煩我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子已經是恩愛十足了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 慶功會的時候也是 尤其是風早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事到如今真是懷疑 為什麼當初就沒有發現他們這麼般配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 很自然嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒想到胡桃會失戀 貞子會得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
